headline: CBRE (CBRE) Valuation Check After 24% One-Year Gain and Rebuilding Share Price Momentum
summary: CBRE Group (CBRE) has quietly outperformed many real estate peers this year, and with the stock up about 24 % over the past year, investors are starting to revisit its long term growth story. See our latest analysis for CBRE Group. At a share price of $160.01, CBRE’s recent 7 day share price return of 2.14% and robust 1 year total shareholder return of 24.12% suggest momentum is gradually rebuilding after a softer quarter.
